com.codemelon.graph.vertex

Interface VisitedVertex

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Vertex
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DfsVertex, EdgeTypeDfsVertex<T>, OrderedDfsVertex
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DirectedDfsVertex, DirectedOrderedDfsVertex

    public interface VisitedVertex
extends Vertex
    Vertex that supports fields for marking discovery and finish times, as required in depth=first search
